comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:52:46.898Z",codex-jellyfin,"The local 10.11.11 server currently serves 429 operations from /api-docs/openapi.json. The implementation remains intentionally resilient: it prefers the authenticated local specification, validates version-matched official stable fallback sources, never forwards credentials off-host, caches only under the private user data directory, and exposes source provenance."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:00:05.640Z",codex-jellyfin,"Official source selected: https://repo.jellyfin.org/files/openapi/stable/jellyfin-openapi-<version>.json; only strictly validated numeric dotted versions may enter the URL."
